OL,3,CLondon is 'cooking', UN chief warns as
OL,4,Che urges countries to cut fossil fuels
OL,6,FLondon is "cooking", the United
OL,7,FNations chief has warned, as he argued
OL,8,Fthat the would cannot double down on
OL,9,Ffossil fuels in the face of
OL,10,Fdevastating climate change.
OL,12,FUN secretary general Antonio Guterres
OL,13,Freferenced Charles Dickens' novel A
OL,14,FTale Of Two Cities in a major address
OL,15,Fat London Climate Action Week as the
OL,16,Fcapital swelters in a severe heatwave.
OL,26,@nD@KOUnD@SO]
