OL,3,CLondon is 'cooking', UN chief warns as
OL,4,Che urges countries to cut fossil fuels
OL,6,FSpeaking at the event on Tuesday, Mr
OL,7,FGuterres said: "Crisis brings clarity
OL,8,Fand here in London ` the city of
OL,9,FDickens ` it is clear that our world
OL,10,Fis facing a 'tale of two crises'.
OL,12,F"A climate crisis is pushing us deeper
OL,13,Ftowards higher temperatures and closer
OL,14,Fto catastrophic tipping points and an
OL,15,Fenergy crisis exposing the folly of a
OL,16,Fworld hooked on hydrocarbons.
OL,18,F"On the surface, these crises may seem
OL,19,Fseparate, but they share the same
OL,20,Fdestructive origin: fossil fuels."
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@bO]
