OL,3,CLondon is 'cooking', UN chief warns as
OL,4,Che urges countries to cut fossil fuels
OL,6,FHis address coincides with an
OL,7,Funprecedented heatwave hitting the UK
OL,8,Fthis week, which has sparked fears
OL,9,Fover the impact of extreme heat on
OL,10,Fhealth, schools, workplaces and
OL,11,Ftransport.
OL,13,FTemperatures are expected to smash the
OL,14,FJune record set in 1976 by several
OL,15,Fdegrees as human-driven climate change
OL,16,Fintensifies the impact of a "heat-
OL,17,Fdome" settling over western Europe.
OL,19,F"London isn't just calling. It's
OL,20,Fcooking," the UN chief said.
OL,26,@xD@]OUyD@EO]{D@AOU|D@IO]
