OL,3,CLondon is 'cooking', UN chief warns as
OL,4,Che urges countries to cut fossil fuels
OL,6,FHe warned that climate chaos is
OL,7,F"accelerating before our eyes" while
OL,8,Fthe arrival of the El Nino warming
OL,9,Fweather phenomenon this summer risks
OL,10,F"blowing the house down" as it
OL,11,Fcompounds the escalating impacts.
